				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$247\pm 3~\text{K}$\end{document}. Throughout the vacuum heat balance test of the orbiter’s FM, MMS storage temperature is around 238 K. At the remote sensing stage shown in Fig. 17b, the operating temperatures of the OSU and EU are both lower than 250 K.

